ue growth is positive, the extremely high forward P/E of 154.44 and low profit margins (3.9%) suggest the stock is overvalued. Technical indicators show the price is trading below both the 50-day and 200-day SMAs, and headlines remain skeptical about the growth trajectory.\n\n    *   JSON only? Yes.\n    *   One action? Yes.\n    *   6-12 month horizon? Yes.", "finish_reason": "stop"}',78360,NULL,'2026-07-16T00:52:20+00:00');
